@startuml
title Event Management - Context Diagram

actor "Browser / Mobile Client" as Client
package "Next.js App" {
  node "Frontend + API routes" as NextApp
}
database "PostgreSQL (DB)" as DB
cloud "External Services\nAuth / Email / SMS" as External
component "Prisma Client" as Prisma

Client --> NextApp : HTTPS
NextApp --> Prisma : ORM calls
Prisma --> DB : SQL
NextApp --> External : Auth / Email

note right of NextApp
  Hosts server-rendered pages
  and API routes
end note

@enduml
